title: Take over Lease. Last month free. Avail Sept 1st
posting_body: ['<URL>/', '10 E 18th', 'St', 'Minneapolis, MN', '55403', 'Are you looking for a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath Apartment in Minneapolis?', 'Looking at Sept time frame?', 'Corner Unit only 1 neighbor.', 'I signed a new 11 month lease that started in 5/1/2022 and ends 4/30/23 but need to move for work relocation purposes and need to find someone to take over the lease.', "Last Month's rent is paid as part of the current lease I signed and you can keep my deposit once you move out or even decide to stay.", 'Pets ok, Garage parking (extra per month).', 'Visit the Nico website to check out the deck, fitness centre etc.', 'Good deal if your looking for a place already and want the last month to be free.', 'Please contact Ryan for any questions.', 'Nico Apartments will do a background check etc to qualify.']
